    <p>FADEL: (Laughter).</p>
    <p>SAVAGE: ...Was in our preschool class. And I mean, I actually knew about it for a year. I didn't tell anyone. But I was obsessed with her butt.</p>
    <p>FADEL: (Laughter).</p>
