    <p>RADHA MUTHIAH: Department of State, Commerce, FDA, FBI, Coast Guard - we just had a woman from the White House. The list goes on.</p>
    <p>STEWART: These aren't the food bank's usual clients, says Muthiah. They normally serve people near or below the poverty level. But...</p>
    <p>MUTHIAH: Having that missed paycheck yesterday, they - you know, they're just worried about where to get their food. And we've had someone say, I'll pay you back after I get my paycheck, but I just need it now.</p>
