    <p>MARTIN: Oh, no.</p>
    <p>PINKETT SMITH: And on that particular episode, I got to learn, you know, about some struggles Willow had been going through.</p>
    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF TV SHOW, "RED TABLE TALK")</p>
