    <p>NICOLE RAMOS: This isn't remain in Mexico. This is stay in Mexico forever.</p>
    <p>RIVLIN-NADLER: The Department of Homeland Security has not responded to a request for comment about when the plan will be implemented. For NPR News, I'm Max Rivlin-Nadler in Tijuana.</p>
