    <p>BOOKER: Or, the president says, he will declare a national emergency to get his border wall - a move that will almost certainly be challenged in the courts.</p>
    <p>(SOUNDBITE OF PHONE RINGING)</p>
    <p>ERIC INGRAM: Hello.</p>
    <p>BOOKER: Hi. It's Brakkton from NPR.</p>
